ble":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这是我今天笑的最开心的一次\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562313490,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3b22cc6cdedf456bf95cf56c71132a99","url_token":"xiao-long-69-68","name":"龙嘉昕","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3b22cc6cdedf456bf95cf56c71132a99","user_type":"people","headline":"机械学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562313490","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546073605,"updated_time":1546183492,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e写在最前:别来我下面两开花，看厌了，见必删。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先回答你的问题:能，而且决不止步于此。可以说这个问题挺荒唐，能问出这个问题说明题主对上清华和证哥猜二者至少其中一个的难度根本没有概念。如果高考上清华的难度是10，竞赛上清华的难度也不过几十，决不上百;而证哥猜的难度是100000+。真的证出哥猜，完全能在全球任一大学数学系直博并出任教授。既然你说自己的方法很简单，先自己给自己发一份，然后给清华大学教授发一份。不用学界普遍认可，只要让教授发现你的研究天赋就足够保送了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，以上不是重点，以下才是。 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 有没有证明哥猜，不仅会彻底改变学一术界的走向，更会彻底改变你的命运;而改变你命运的力量来自于网络暴力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎早已不是所谓精英的专场。知乎注册门槛并没有限制学历、品行、性格。随着网络普及，各方面素质参差不齐的用户涌入知乎，网络暴力也大量渗入。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在你拥有两万多关注，我以两万来算。如果你证明了哥猜，你会保有15000~18000关注，并获得直博机会，从事研究工作，几年之内有望十万关注。听起来挺辉煌吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可如果你没有证明哥猜呢？(包括没有准时发证明和证明有误。)视你犯错误水平的高低(高中水平到数学系教授水平)，你能保有100~5000关注，有2000~5000人会在第一时间嘲讽辱骂你(是的，有些人就算你水平比他高，只要你失败了，他就会开骂。)，还有80~4500人会持续在你的提问、回答下嘲讽辱骂你，这些你真的能承受吗？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562733426,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"dc3cb7a6b1e2bb51c1e939d29b2ca430","url_token":"bai-san-71","name":"小池一别","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ef7cec86525d37ea26a84ecd0ca022c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ef7cec86525d37ea26a84ecd0ca022c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/dc3cb7a6b1e2bb51c1e939d29b2ca430","user_type":"people","headline":"「杨超越挑战赛发起者，详见想法」","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562733426","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546140125,"updated_time":1546141003,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e对，高中生解出哥猜是万无可能的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e所以，在这个问题下嘲讽题主是绝对安全的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e是吗？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主呢，不管他是哗众取宠也好，真的不自量力也好，至少他的语言还算平和，对各位明显带有嘲讽和蔑视的评论我看他并不怎么回击。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我姑且认为这是一个有些理智的人。（说实话，比一部分答题的人更理智）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主其实讲的很明白：他不确定自己一定证对了，但他“证明出来了”。那么他其实就是到知乎上征求一些意见。对嘲讽简单回复一下，然后默默收藏有价值的回复（对，他竟然真的在记那些邮箱和电话）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这个问题下的很多答主，怎么说呢？就仿佛知乎盛产的一类人，其实他也不是内行，但是他们不会放过任何一个安全的出言嘲讽的机会。就像现在，一个高中生不自量力的证明哥猜，万无可能，所以可以开始嘲了，绝对安全。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可是确实如此吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当嘲讽成为习惯，总有一天你会踩中真东西，总有一天万无可能之事会在“万”外发生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e甚至这个表面上高中生的题主，谁又知道他是不是某个研究群体意识的学者呢？也许他专门为了研究“哗众取宠”，以及“所有人都踩了一脚我也来踩一脚”这种事呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，嘲讽被打脸是最微不足道的事了，毕竟嘲讽的快乐是敲敲键盘就能得到了。而讽刺力的回馈隔着网线反不到大家的现实生活中嘛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后回到问题，我是不信题主能证出来的，但是如果你真证对了，我为你鼓掌。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563035516,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563035516","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546175255,"updated_time":1546175255,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2018最感动我的一件事，就是看到那么多说出 “我相信你” “我们相信你” “我们为什么不相信他” “你们为什么不相信他”的\u003cb\u003e善良\u003c/b\u003e的答主\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他们数学水平极高，反感学术欺压，决定义无反顾地声援一个天才的高中生，他们以正义之名，高喊:“打倒数学！”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哎呀喊错了，是“打倒学术欺压！\u003cb\u003e”\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我被这种精神深深的打动了，\u003cb\u003e是什么力量，让他们勇敢地站出来，为题主，为每一个有数学梦的人发声？！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e是革命的大无畏精神啊！！！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我眼含热泪，他们的名字，为了在以后的\u003cb\u003e科学类问题\u003c/b\u003e下，看到他们，就毫不犹豫地、深情地点下小小的三角……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e向你们致以崇高的敬意！！！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561038092,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561038092","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a2fa683a989b47349d465099522dd697_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545910191,"updated_time":1545990312,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e修改一下，支持者受众又扩大了呢，不过文化水平还是很稳定啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4ebd04c0972da80fdc3531553695e706_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4ebd04c0972da80fdc3531553695e706_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4ebd04c0972da80fdc3531553695e706_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2248'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4ebd04c0972da80fdc3531553695e706_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox