吃白糖吃白糖。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559843105,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559843105","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545787807,"updated_time":1545787807,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e估计了题主提问时间，又看了清华北大的字眼，我基本可以理解题主的心情啦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很正常的，觉得考清北压力大，就希望通过一些压力看起来不是那么大的方式去实现自己的梦想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过抱歉的是，投机取巧的道路是不存在的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e给题主的建议，就像其它回答说的，如果题主自认为有证明哥德巴赫猜想的能力，以这种智商和天赋，高考和竞赛程度基本不在话下。建议题主去买本竞赛的数论书，感受一下数论的难度，直观的想象一下哥德巴赫猜想的难度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第二呢，是对题主的忠告，有这闲工夫，赶紧准备高考去。梦里的日行万里比不上实际的脚迈一步。寄希望于这种事情，还不如去解决一两道题你认为难得不得了的高考压轴题，后者在现阶段乃至你很长的一段岁月中，价值都比前者大的多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第三，作为曾经的高考生，说句心底话。高中的时候，想考清北很正常。但最重要的是摆平心态，把目标适当的放在自己踮踮脚就能够到的高度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你的前人，数学届无数无数的前辈，许许多多智商悟性灵气皆高的不可想象的人，尽毕生之功，却在解决哥德巴赫猜想的道路上折戟而归，穷数学届之力，才走到陈景润的程度。题主，你觉得呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561181170,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561181170","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-03438c97383a985dddea5349397fc610_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545924196,"updated_time":1545924196,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e看不下去一堆圣人说不要打击题主。你想鼓励就鼓励，也别要求别人温柔好吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e谁是闲着没事哄着他玩呢？他既然敢出来吸引流量，就要承担后果。又没有人刀架他脖子上逼着他做这一切。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外题主\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63a5b35a7728603d4e054bffecb77cd6_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1668\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63a5b35a7728603d4e054bffecb77cd6_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63a5b35a7728603d4e054bffecb77cd6_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1668'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1668\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63a5b35a7728603d4e054bffecb77cd6_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63a5b35a7728603d4e054bffecb77cd6_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63a5b35a7728603d4e054bffecb77cd6_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这种语气怎么看都像是骗关注啊？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560452363,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560452363","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545838842,"updated_time":1545897060,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e妈呀这题目居然这么多人关注。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个问题本身不值一提。不过有意思的是居然还有朋友认为题主乐于思考勇于尝试。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e讲道理，要是题主能直接发出自己的“证明”过程，并且虚心求教错误所在的话，还勉强可以鼓励一下。可现实是题主采取了低级的炒作方式，从ta的言行中看不到一丝对数学的敬畏，可以说其表现和“民科”只差一线，这不值得任何鼓励和肯定。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，虽然八成这只是一场无聊的钓鱼，但是也不能排除题主真的是中二高中生的可能性嘛，我就把你往好了想想吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主真的是高中生，我建议不要等到元旦了，现在就把“证明”发出来吧，会有一大堆人乐意给你指出错误的，弄明白自己错在哪之后就好好准备高考，别想那些有的没的。乐于思考是好的，但是以后对数学多点敬畏，再对什么猜想有了想法就虚心的找人问问，你们老师就行，拉不下脸的话问网友也成。以后不要再做愚蠢的事了。还有，对于答案里的鼓励别当真，对嘲讽也别太往心里去，虽然有的嘲讽确实不太合适，不过自己犯蠢被嘲讽两句也正常。况且又没人知道你是谁，换个知乎账号咱又是一条好汉对吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e补充：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果是炒作钓鱼，赌五毛钱结局会是题主认错，表示以后虚心学习，然后收获一波鼓励和关注...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但愿事实不是如此吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过无论哪种情况，作为吃瓜群众最好的选择是别给题主太多鼓励也别嘲讽的太过就是了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e＝＝\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560427612,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":3065